<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">Today, I=E2=80=99m thrilled to =
announce the second installment of this groundbreaking series. This time, w=
e=E2=80=99re focusing on how executives and industry insiders are navigatin=
g the post-election economic landscape: the potential impact of tariffs, tr=
ade wars, deregulation, changing tax regimes, and a hyper-charged political=
 climate. We=E2=80=99re also diving more deeply into how our audience of me=
dia consumers and producers, alike, are engaging with an entertainment indu=
stry and information space that is more fractured than ever.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0;">But remember, this is meant to be=C2=A0<em>fun</em>=
=2E The anonymous survey only takes a f=
ew minutes to complete, and just like=20=
the first time, your responses will be synthesized by my partner=C2=A0<stro=
ng>Baratunde Thurston</strong>, who will sift through the data and surface =
the most relevant and surprising insights. This data provides the sort of l=
andscape analysis that other companies outsource to consulting firms. Here =
at Puck, it=E2=80=99s just another benefit of membership. Thanks for your t=
ime, and I hope you=E2=80=99re as excited as I am to dig into the resultss.=
